These attributes are ONLY usable on the `this` pointer in a `combodata script`.

<h3>int X;
int Y;
int Layer;
int Pos;</h3>
Read-only. Gives the X, Y, Layer, and Combo Pos of the combo running this script.

The `FileSystem->` pointer holds misc functions related to files and directories.

Paths are often relative to a 'quest specific directory', which is at "[zc root]/files/[quest name]/"

Related: ${fileptr|file}, ${directoryptr|directory}
